{
  "stem": "353.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this was my finish story in-- in Brinnlitz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I have to come back to something what I didn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a time in Brinnlitz where people who came from Budzyn, Majdanek, very tough guys, very tough guys.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were officers in Polish army, Jews from the Polish army.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the end of the war, they kicked them into the concentration camps, Russian boys.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they create a underground organization-- partisans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And one of those people came to me-- this was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] before-- excuse me-- [BACKGROUND NOISE]",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--before I burn out the light in the-- Yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--In the [? shop. ?] And they ask me if I want to join the underground.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I said yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why not?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The whole life I went through, I'm going to go again in another few-- few years.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know how long going to take.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So what happened, I knew nobody.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew only five people in my unit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The five-- there was five units.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I knew there was five units.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I-- I know only five people in my unit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, just five people in each unit?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Five people in a unit.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the whole thing was five units to five people, 25 people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, this is in the resistance group?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in the resistance group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what-- what we did, we were breaking into magazines, to all kind of things, and bringing out, helping people with-- with food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 9 SECONDS] the five people in the unit, you couldn't know the other five, because if the Gestapo caught you, so you could, if they press on you, you could give up only five.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The other five you didn't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
